OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early mist and fog patches
OL,6,Fwill quickly clear this morning to
OL,7,Fleave blue skies. Winds will
OL,8,Fstrengthen in the south but it will
OL,9,Ffeel warm in any sheltered spots.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStaying dry tonight with
OL,12,Flargely clear skies, although a veil
OL,13,Fof high cloud will move over at times.
OL,14,FA patchy rural frost is possible in
OL,15,Fthe coldest spots.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FAnother dry and sunny day
OL,18,Facross the region. After a chilly
OL,19,Fstart, it will warm up through the
OL,20,Fday, although a brisk wind will make
OL,21,Fit feel fresh in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
